******MountSMB*******

Select either ftp or smb, if you select smb then you can either enter an IP, or scan for smb servers in your current workgroup and select a server from the drop down list.

Enter an IP into the box and press enter the drop down will then be populated with the various shares.

Enter a username or leave blank for anonymous login, if no user name is supplied the password will be ignored.
Unmount as normal.

On first run the username is filled in with the users login name.
Username, password and IP addrerss are remembered ( even if left blank ).

Bugs and stuff to:
kdhedger@yahoo.co.uk

